    "name": "traffic_light_state",
    "type": "string",
    "description": "The new state of the traffic light, for 'vehicle' lights, can be 'red', 'green', 'yellow', or 'hazard'; for 'pedestrian' lights, can be 'walk', 'stop', or 'flashing'.",
